{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/jason-momoa-lobo-dc-comics/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Apa Jadinya Kalau Jason Momoa Berperan Sebagai Lobo?","content":"<p>Saat ini nama Jason Momoa dan Aquaman merupakan tema pembicaraan yang sedang <em>hot</em> di kalangan penggemar komik dan film (<em>superheroes</em>) dunia.</p>\n<p>Dan keduanya memang layak jadi bahan pembicaraan. Jason Momoa secara gemilang berhasil menghidupkan peran sosok jagoan <em>superhero</em> DC Comics yang dulu, secara tradisional, tidak terlalu mengilap reputasinya. Tidak seperti Superman, Batman, Wonder Woman, dan bahkan The Flash. <em>Aquaman was a joke</em>. Aquaman dulu lebih sebagai sosok komedik di antara para <em>superhero</em> DC Comics lain. Sebagian besar alasan karena kemampuan yang dianggap tidak keren karena hanya berlaku di air / lautan saja.</p>\n<p>Film solo Aquaman (setelah sebelumnya ‘pemanasan’ di film “Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice serta “Justice League”) dengan pemeran utama Jason Momoa mengubah citra Aquaman dengan sempurna. Dari jagoan nggak diperhitungkan sebagai sosok penting menjadi <em>superhero</em> yang membuat semua orang, fans komik atau tidak, terpesona.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52600\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52600\" data-attachment-id=\"52600\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jason-momoa-lobo-dc-comics/attachment/01-jason-momoa-lobo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-jason-momoa-lobo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52600\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" alt=\"Film Aquaman (Sumber: Cleveland)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52600\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Film Aquaman (Sumber: Cleveland)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>Baca juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jason-momoa-aktor-macho-yang-tak-hanya-jadi-aquaman-saja-penampilan-polos-tanpa-kumisnya-bikin-pangling/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Jason Momoa, Aktor Macho yang Tak Hanya Jadi Aquaman Saja. Penampilan Polos Tanpa Kumisnya Bikin Pangling!</a></strong></p>\n<p>Jason Momoa mungkin sudah ditakdirkan untuk menghidupkan sosok fiksi fantasi menjadi nyata dengan citra <em>macho</em>, gahar dan ‘laki banget’ ?</p>\n<p>Ini sudah terlihat di peran-peran yang dia lakukan sebelumnya; seperti Ronon Dex di serial TV “Stargate Atlantis” atau di serial TV yang <em>arguably</em> melambungkan nama dan citra Jason Momoa sebagai <em>total badass</em>: “Game of Thrones”.</p>\n<p>Peran Momoa sebagai Khal Drogo sangat <em>memorable</em> walau hanya untuk satu <em>season</em>. Yang nge-fans Jason Momoa sebelum film Aquaman bisa jadi mulai nge-fans dia saat berperan di Game of Thrones itu.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52601\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52601\" data-attachment-id=\"52601\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jason-momoa-lobo-dc-comics/attachment/02-jason-momoa-lobo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-jason-momoa-lobo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52601\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" alt=\"Jason Momoa sebagai Khal Drogo (Sumber: Joe.ie)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52601\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Jason Momoa sebagai Khal Drogo (Sumber: Joe.ie)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>Baca juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/inilah-alasan-mengapa-serial-tv-game-thrones-sangat-populer-penasaran/\">Inilah Alasan Mengapa Serial TV Game Of Thrones Sangat Populer. Penasaran?</a></strong></p>\n<p>Nah… Karena kemampuan Jason Momoa membangun citra <em>macho</em> itulah, muncul pemikiran dan opini di kalangan penggemar komik (terutama komik DC Comics) kalau sebenarnya Jason Momoa akan lebih ideal berperan sebagai “Lobo” ketimbang “Aquaman”.</p>\n<p>Mengapa begitu? Siapa Lobo ini?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52602\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52602\" data-attachment-id=\"52602\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jason-momoa-lobo-dc-comics/attachment/03-jason-momoa-lobo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-jason-momoa-lobo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52602\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" alt=\"Lobo. Karakter komik DC Comics (Sumber: Den Of Geek)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52602\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lobo. Karakter komik DC Comics (Sumber: Den Of Geek)</p></div></p>\n<p>Lobo merupakan karakter DC Comics ciptaan Roger Slifer &amp; Keith Giffen yang muncul perdana di serial “Omega Men #3” bulan Juni tahun 1983. Karakter ini diciptakan sebagai <em>bandit/supervillain</em> alias antagonis. Dia adalah <em>alien</em> dari planet Czarnia dengan penampilan sangar dan profesi sebagai pemburu buronan berhadiah yang beroperasi antar planet.</p>\n<p>Dengan body gede, rambut gondrong serta penampilan sangar, Lobo mulai merambah dunia komik DC di era ‘80an. Namun sayang penulisan cerita untuk karakter ini tidak mampu menghidupkan Lobo agar menarik sehingga ‘karir’ nya sempat meredup. Namun tidak terlalu lama, karena kemudian ia mengalami kondisi <em>‘rebranding’</em> menjadi tokoh <em>antihero</em>: alias bukan antagonis namun juga bukan tokoh baik/protagonis.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52603\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52603\" data-attachment-id=\"52603\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jason-momoa-lobo-dc-comics/attachment/04-jason-momoa-lobo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-jason-momoa-lobo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52603\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" alt=\"Debut Lobo ada di komik ini (Sumber: eBay)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52603\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Debut Lobo ada di komik ini (Sumber: eBay)</p></div></p>\n<p>Menjadikan Lobo sebagai karakter <em>antihero</em> merupakan keputusan tepat karena kemudian di era ‘90an karakter ini semakin dikenal dan sering menjadi <em>cameo</em> atau melakukan <em>cross-over</em> dengan karakter komik DC lain.</p>\n<p>Lobo cari ribut dengan Superman? Pernah!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52604\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52604\" data-attachment-id=\"52604\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jason-momoa-lobo-dc-comics/attachment/05-jason-momoa-lobo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-jason-momoa-lobo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52604\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: Wikia)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52604\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: Wikia)</p></div></p>\n<p>Dia juga sempat pernah mendapatkan Red Lantern Ring, yang merupakan <em>item</em> <em>supervillain</em> serial “Green Lantern”.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52605\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52605\" data-attachment-id=\"52605\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jason-momoa-lobo-dc-comics/attachment/06-jason-momoa-lobo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-jason-momoa-lobo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52605\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: Comicvine Gamespot)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52605\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: Comicvine Gamespot)</p></div></p>\n<p>Seperti kebiasaan komik-komik <em>franchise </em>Amerika, desain Lobo mengalami perubahan-perubahan sejak pertama muncul tahun 1983 namun secara prinsip desain karakternya tetap mengacu pada karakteristik <em>macho</em>, <em>brute</em> dengan citra <em>badass</em> alias jagoan sangar.</p>\n<p>Kulit pucat seperti warna kapur papan tulis, ekspresi wajah bengis serta cerutu di bibir, Lobo merupakan personifikasi seorang karakter <em>antihero</em> yang sulit untuk dibenci walau jelas ngeselin.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52606\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52606\" data-attachment-id=\"52606\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jason-momoa-lobo-dc-comics/attachment/07-jason-momoa-lobo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-jason-momoa-lobo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52606\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" alt=\"Konsep desain Lobo dari Kenneth Rocafort (Sumber: Concept Art World)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52606\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Konsep desain Lobo dari Kenneth Rocafort (Sumber: Concept Art World)</p></div></p>\n<p>Jadi saat Jason Momoa, yang secara <em>default</em> memiliki tongkrongan khas Lobo, ditunjuk sebagai Arthur Curry alias Aquaman, beberapa suara terdengar tidak terlalu menyetujui hal itu.</p>\n<p>Memang Aquaman di versi modern (New 52 &amp; Rebirth) memiliki desain lebih <em>macho</em> ketimbang versi-versi awal Aquaman yang klimis dan ‘culun’. Desain modern Aquaman <em>matching</em> dengan tongkrongan Jason Momoa secara <em>default</em>. Brewok, gondrong, dengan <em>body</em> segede gaban. Dan hasil akhir film Aquaman (termasuk di Batman v Superman &amp; Justice League) membuktikan kalau penunjukan Jason Momoa sebagai Aquaman adalah keputusan tepat.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52607\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52607\" data-attachment-id=\"52607\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jason-momoa-lobo-dc-comics/attachment/08-jason-momoa-lobo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"08-jason-momoa-lobo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52607\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" alt=\"Aquaman versi komik &amp; film (Sumber: What Culture)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52607\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Aquaman versi komik &amp; film (Sumber: What Culture)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>Baca juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/citra-aquaman-lebih-bersinar-di-film-justice-league-yes-no/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Citra Aquaman Lebih Bersinar Di Film Justice League? Yes or No?</a></strong></p>\n<p>Tapi bagaimana kalau seandainya dia ditunjuk memerankan Lobo ketimbang Aquaman?</p>\n<p>Menurut saya hasilnya akan sama keren; walau itu tergantung skenario dan pengarahan yang diterima oleh Momoa. Film Aquaman keren karena ditangani dengan bagus oleh James Wan. Jika film Lobo dibuat, kita tidak tahu siapa yang akan ditunjuk oleh DC Comics/Warner Bros. sebagai sutradara.</p>\n<p>Begitu pula dengan skenario yang akan digunakan. Apakah dari <em>origins</em> asli Lobo tahun 1983, atau interpretasi lebih modern dari karkater ini?</p>\n<p>Saya tidak terlalu kuatir dengan akting Momoa jika berperan sebagai Lobo. Karena dia bukan sekedar aktor yang hanya berbekal <em>body</em> gede atau wajah ganteng. Berperan sebagai <em>antihero</em> seperti Lobo tidak akan jadi persoalan serius untuk Jason Momoa.</p>\n<p>Tapi karena Momoa kini sudah identik, dan bahkan menurut saya sudah menciptakan sebuah <em>“Gold Standard”</em> untuk Aquaman (seperti yang sudah sukses dilakukan Robert Downey Jr. “Iron Man” atau Chris Hemsworth “Thor”), bakal sulit melihat film Aquaman jika bukan diperankan oleh Jason Momoa di masa depan nanti. Sehingga mustahil melihat dia berperan sebagai Lobo; walaupun peran itu dikatakan sangat cocok untuknya.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/aquaman-eksperimen-indah-dan-mengerikan-dari-james-wan/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Aquaman: Eksperimen Indah dan Mengerikan Dari James Wan</a></strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52608\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52608\" data-attachment-id=\"52608\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jason-momoa-lobo-dc-comics/attachment/09-jason-momoa-lobo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"09-jason-momoa-lobo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52608\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" alt=\"Sepertinya memang cocok? (Sumber: Comicvine Gamespot)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52608\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sepertinya memang cocok? (Sumber: Comicvine Gamespot)</p></div></p>\n<p>Akan sulit bagi Jason Momoa untuk sekaligus menciptakan citra dua karakter komik jagoan yang berasal dari sindikasi sama.</p>\n<p>Aquaman dan Lobo adalah IP DC Comics. Jadi akan aneh jika Aquaman dan Lobo diperankan oleh aktor yang sama. Walaupun kasus seperti itu pernah dialami oleh Marvel untuk karakter “Human Torch” dan “Captain America”, yang mana pernah diperankan oleh aktor yang sama: Chris Evans. Tapi kini peran Human Torch ada di tangan Michael B. Jordan. Yang juga pernah berperan di film “Black Panther” sebagai Killmonger. Tapi perannya sebagai Killmonger sudah selesai. Dan (sepertinya) tidak mungkin kembali.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52609\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52609\" data-attachment-id=\"52609\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jason-momoa-lobo-dc-comics/attachment/10-jason-momoa-lobo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"10-jason-momoa-lobo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52609\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" alt=\"“Human Torch” Chris Evan x Human Torch Michael B. Jordan (Sumber: Reddit)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52609\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">“Human Torch” Chris Evan x Human Torch Michael B. Jordan (Sumber: Reddit)</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>Baca juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/artis-ini-gak-malu-ngaku-sebagai-otaku/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Artis Ini Gak Malu Ngaku Sebagai Otaku!</a></strong></p>\n<p>Tapi itu di Marvel. Sementara situasi yang sama belum tentu terjadi di DC Comics.</p>\n<p>Jadi seberapa greget seandainya Jason Momoa berperan sebagai Lobo? Tentu akan greget banget. Saya yakin Momoa akan menghidupkan Lobo dengan keren di layar film. Tidak diragukan.</p>\n<p>Namun saat ini Jason Momoa adalah Arthur Curry alias Aquaman. Raja Tujuh Samudera dari Atlantis. Dan dia melakukan pekerjaan itu dengan sangat baik. Sehingga bisa dipastikan kalau di film Aquaman berikutnya (atau film dimana Aquaman muncul) Jason Momoa akan mengulangi peran tersebut.</p>\n<p>Sehingga sulit bagi Momoa untuk berperan ganda sebagai Lobo selagi publik masih menyukainya sebagai Aquaman.</p>\n<p>Kalau begitu, siapa yang bisa cocok memerankan Lobo seandainya DC Comics &amp; Warner Bros. tiba-tiba membuat film Lobo?</p>\n<p>Salah satu teman media sosial saya mengatakan “Ron Perlman!”. Perlman sendiri bukan aktor asing di peran <em>superhero/antihero</em> karena pernah berperan sebagai “Hellboy”. Jika di dandani dengan <em>make-up</em> yang tepat, mungkin dia cocok berperan sebagai Lobo? Mungkin. Tapi andaikan bukan Josh Brolin, Ron Perlman kayaknya oke jika berperan menjadi Cable-nya “Deadpool” walau usianya tidak lagi muda.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52610\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52610\" data-attachment-id=\"52610\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jason-momoa-lobo-dc-comics/attachment/11-jason-momoa-lobo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/11-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"11-jason-momoa-lobo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/11-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/11-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52610\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/11-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" alt=\"Ron Perlman &amp; Cable (Sumber: Screen Rant)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/11-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/11-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52610\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ron Perlman &amp; Cable (Sumber: Screen Rant)</p></div></p>\n<p>Tapi tak hanya Ron Perlman. Bagaimana dengan aktor-aktor lain seperti di foto berikut?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52611\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52611\" data-attachment-id=\"52611\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jason-momoa-lobo-dc-comics/attachment/12-jason-momoa-lobo/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/12-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"12-jason-momoa-lobo\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/12-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/12-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52611\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/12-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: Jolygram)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/12-jason-momoa-lobo.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/12-jason-momoa-lobo-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52611\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: Jolygram)</p></div></p>\n<p>Menurut kamu sendiri bagaimana? Suarakan pendapatmu!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"d557e9e7-06a5-5272-9ef8-f29763b18504"}}}